r 24 hours with a tagline \"Just having someone understanding to talk to can save a life\".<ref>[http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/madurai/24-hour-helpline-launched-for-LGBTs-in-Madurai/articleshow/20994000.cms?referral=PM \"24-hour helpline launched for LGBTs in Madurai\"], ''Times of India'', July 10, 2015.</ref>\n* {{flagicon|United Kingdom}} [https://BritishAsianLGBTI.org British Asian LGBTI] Online Support Group Founded by Siddhi Joshi on 27th September 2013 <ref>[https://BritishAsianLGBTI.org British Asian LGBTI]</ref>\n* {{flagicon|Nepal}} Supreme Court of Nepal ruling for the introduction of a transgender category for people obtaining their citizenship certificates. People can register as a third gender when completing the certificates which serve as national identity cards required to open bank accounts, sell and buy property, and get a passport.<ref name=desiq-2013-timeline />\n* {{flagicon|India}} On December 11, 2013, Supreme Court of India reinstates [[Section 377 of the Indian Penal Code]], overruling the 2009 Delhi High Court Judgement<ref name=desiq-2013-timeline />\n* {{flagicon|United States}} First Khush DC women's membership meeting<ref name=desiq-2013-timeline />\n* {{flagicon|India}} First high-school LGBTQIA alliance in India: Breaking Barriers at Tagore International, New Delhi<ref name=desiq-2013-timeline /><ref name=orinam-campus-initiatives />\n* {{flagicon|Malaysia}} \"You and I\" campaign for trans people and allies starts in Malaysia<ref name=desiq-2013-timeline />\n* {{flagicon|Canada}} Trikone Toronto launches<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://allevents.in/toronto/trikone-toronto-launch-meet-and-greet/219210288229439|title = Trikone Toronto Launch Meet & Greet|accessdate = |website = |last = |first = }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://trikonetoronto.blogspot.com/2013/05/welcome-to-trikone-toronto.html|title = Welcome to TRIKONE TORONTO|date = May 6, 2013|accessdate = May 10, 2015|website = Trikone Toronto|publisher = Trikone Toronto